      <title>特鲁多的春季预算让加拿大企业担心新税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/trudeau-s-spring-budget-has-canadian-firms-worried-about-new-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰（Chrystia Freeland）即将推出的预算让加拿大商界的一些人担心，税收将增加，以抵消新的政府支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/trudeau-s-spring-budget-has-canadian-firms-worried-about-new-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
