      <title>交易员加大欧洲央行降息押注，押注经济前景黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/traders-step-up-ecb-rate-cut-bets-on-softer-inflation-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政策制定者在最新预测中概述了欧元区更加黯淡的经济前景后，交易员押注欧洲央行今年将进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/traders-step-up-ecb-rate-cut-bets-on-softer-inflation-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀疲软引发降息前景，欧洲央行维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/ecb-interest-rates-held-as-weaker-inflation-raises-prospect-of-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行第四次会议维持利率不变，通胀和经济增长前景疲软增强了从 6 月份开始降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/ecb-interest-rates-held-as-weaker-inflation-raises-prospect-of-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度禁止 JM Financial 管理公共债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-bars-jm-financial-from-managing-public-debt-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据印度资本市场监管机构通过的初步命令，印度资本市场监管机构已禁止 JM Financial Ltd. 担任印度公司任何新公开发行债务的管理人，理由是该公司涉嫌不公平贸易行为和违反商业银行家行为准则。印度证券交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-bars-jm-financial-from-managing-public-debt-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 12:56:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会表示，致命的船只袭击意味着红海航行需要重新思考</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deadly-ship-attack-means-red-sea-voyages-need-re-think-nautilus-union-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个主要运输联盟敦促全面停止穿越红海的商船，并在胡塞武装袭击导致三名水手死亡后，进一步呼吁船只重新考虑航行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deadly-ship-attack-means-red-sea-voyages-need-re-think-nautilus-union-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 12:14:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度打击IPO融资扰乱市场，黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-roils-market-with-new-crackdowns-on-ipo-financing-gold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于陷入印度对该行业不断扩大的打击的金融公司来说，这又是令人心碎的一周，因为监管机构实施了新的限制，这些限制可能会抑制贷款，并抑制蓬勃发展的首次公开募股市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-roils-market-with-new-crackdowns-on-ipo-financing-gold</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行欧洲股市基准涨幅超过 500 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/european-stocks-ease-from-record-as-focus-turns-to-ecb-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行疲软的通胀前景增强了降息预期，欧洲股市延续涨势，基准指数刷新500点以上纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/european-stocks-ease-from-record-as-focus-turns-to-ecb-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔之前股市上涨；欧洲央行后欧元下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在杰罗姆·鲍威尔的证词和周五的就业数据公布之前，华尔街交易员没有进行大额押注。由于欧洲央行维持利率稳定并降低通胀预期，欧元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
